Package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.tab

Class TabServiceImpl

java.lang.Object
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.base.AbstractComponentService<TabComponentType,Tab>
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.tab.TabServiceImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
ButtonService, TabService, TableInsertion
public class TabServiceImpl extends AbstractComponentService<TabComponentType,Tab> implements TabService
Implementation of the TabService interface, offering functionality for tab interactions such as clicking, verifying if tabs are enabled, visible, or selected. Extends AbstractComponentService to manage creation and retrieval of Tab instances.

This class references TabComponentType to determine the specific tab component, ensuring consistent handling of tab-based elements across different UI designs.
